From the delicious breakfast  to scrumptious lunch,  dinner and desserts - this place is top notch.  Ambiance is lovely, people are genuine and heartwarming.  This is a place you want to come back to time and again.  Don't miss this sweet spot in the heart of our vibrant borough of Brooklyn.  Come in and enjoy, have a private party or order for your off premise event.  You cannot go wrong here!!
